title: Freedom From Competition | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Freedom From Competition | Joel Osteen
description:
We weren't created to live in constant comparison with one another. You don't have to try to keep up with anyone—God will make sure you get where you're supposed to be. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
